-------------------- 
Restored to MP3 from his original tapes
SONY UX chrome class
The tapes were recorded using 
- 1 double deck Dj CD player
- 1 vinyl turntable + improvised pitch resistor
- 6 channel analog stereo mixer box
- 1 Sherwood cassette deck
I hope I have time to remaster or improve them someday.
